title: Resurrection: Volcom In Medellin - TransWorld SKATEboarding
description: Resurrection is a chance to watch skateboarding from past TransWorld features you may have forgotten about or never seen to begin with re-edited. Here's a hefty portion of the Volcom team in 2011.
